Dialogue: 1,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これで準備は完了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いつでもこの建物を崩落させられる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,魔力　結構余裕あるな
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.84,0:00:21.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これなら　もしライオスたちに何かあっても　カバーできる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.88,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いいんだよね　これで
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.71,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,魔力を使い切って竜を気絶させる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,みんなの命を懸けて　当たるかわからない爆発魔法で狙うより
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,建物の下敷きにしたほうがずっと確実
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,うん　絶対このほうがいい
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.23,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,落ち着いて
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.84,0:00:48.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私は私の仕事に集中しなくちゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.87,0:00:51.30,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,絶対成功させる
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.13,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,待っててね　ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気付いた
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.04,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,走れ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.92,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,速い速い
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ちなみに　炎竜は最速で時速60キロ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.91,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,先に言え
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,地形で制御できてる　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,次の角を右へ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.67,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この直線で火の息を誘う
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.95,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜は体内にためた燃料に舌打ちで着火することで　炎を吐く
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.22,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,拘束したとき暴れないよう
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.09,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,道中ですべての燃料を排出させる
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,タンギングだ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.07,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,来るぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんて熱量だ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.11,0:03:40.75,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,だが
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.48,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,鍋と魔術のおかげで耐えられる
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よし　これならいけ…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.37,0:03:55.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.75,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,鍋の熱が…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.00,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,均一に広がって
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あっつ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.00,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あれで毎日センシが料理してるんだから
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,てっきり竜の炎は特別に弾くのかと
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.09,0:04:24.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ナマリ曰く　アダマントは竜の攻撃をすべて防ぐという話だったが
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.03,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,アイツ適当なこと言ったな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,言ってない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,また来る
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.88,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかたない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ルート変更だ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.98,0:04:44.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ウソ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.13,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう来た
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.92,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,早くない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,二手に分かれるって作戦は
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私　予定どおりやっていいの
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ええい　わからん
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もうやっちゃう
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ウソウソウソ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,まったく効いてないし
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.12,0:05:57.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,動くな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,逆鱗がすぐそこだ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あと少し踏み込めば
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,届く
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,に…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,逃げやがった
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,クソ　ケン助
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.30,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,やはり所詮は魔物…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.09,0:06:31.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,おま…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　チルチャック　立て
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,上だ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.98,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,腹部に潜り込め
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　テメエ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.92,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,悪かった　悪かったから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,クソ　共通語は罵倒の語彙が少なすぎる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ポンザ　トロルド　ウネルマ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんだかよくわからない言語で罵られている
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうすんだ　こっから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,怒ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すごく怒ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.01,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかたない　尻尾の側から逃げ…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.67,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,だめだ　危険だ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.49,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,俺たち一生股ぐらから出られないんじゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.88,0:07:09.80,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,だめだ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.95,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,こんな簡単な詠唱じゃ効果がない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.11,0:07:12.88,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,集中
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.43,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,何やってんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.79,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,唯一の武器が粉々に…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうすんだ　こっから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかたない　これを使え
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.92,0:07:36.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,やっぱりそれ　本当に特別な金属なのか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あらゆる魔物の骨や皮をたち
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.22,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ワシが一日も欠かさず手入れをしてきた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この世に２つとないかもしれない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ミスリル製の包丁じゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ミスリル？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マジかよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ナマリに見せてやりたかった
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.96,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,アイツ　場合によっちゃセンシを殺すぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんとなくそういう感じはしたので　黙っていた
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.71,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,このっ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.96,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,本当にウロコを貫通した
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.84,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかし　この刀身ではどこを斬りつけようが
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.70,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,致命傷など与えることはできないのでは
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.97,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうしよう　どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.30,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,作戦は失敗したってことだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それとも何か別の作戦中
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いったいどうしたら
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,迷ってる場合じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,下がれ　下がれ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.99,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どんどん武器が遠くなっていく
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,このまま後退すると広場に出ちまう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.99,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そしたら火の息で消し炭だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ワシが竜の気を引こう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よせ　危険だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.30,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　もうわかっているだろう
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今までお前が食ってきた魔物の中に
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.51,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,死力を尽くさないものがいたか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ここでは　食うか食われるか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,必死にならなければ　食われるのはこちらだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,腹をくくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.48,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,センシ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.13,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,セン…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.81,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,バカ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.20,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,お前が飛び出しちゃ意味ないだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.07,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,お前はいったん引け
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.93,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マルシルとなんとかしろ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.99,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,おい　生きてるか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今どけてやる…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.49,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,動けるか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.53,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なんか地面にくっついて…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.16,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どけ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.17,0:10:08.20,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すぐ戻る
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,センシ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.80,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,立てって
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,セン…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すまん　マルシル
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,こんな所にいるとは
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.71,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,魔法効いてるみたいでよかった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今どうなってるの
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.53,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,２人は
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.07,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マズいことになった
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,立てた作戦全部失敗だ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,２人は今　竜の足元で気絶してる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.87,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どどど…　どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そうか　私の魔法しかないか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜は手負いで凶暴になってる
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,近づくのも　視野に入るのも危険だ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.80,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,でもでも　早くなんとかしないと
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,上に向かう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ど…　どうするの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.09,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜の顔の高さまで行って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,俺は鍋に乗り
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.78,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マルシルがそれを爆発させる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.09,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜は左目が潰れてる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,左側から近づけば
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.75,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気付かれずに飛び移ることができるはず
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.87,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,以前　マルシルも同じことをやったろう
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ウンディーネと戦ったとき
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.14,0:11:30.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あのときは　水と水上歩行があったから
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,今回は防御魔法と鍋がある
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そのあとは
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,頭にしがみついたままどうやって逆鱗を狙うの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そこは多少考えがある
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう失敗できないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そのつもりはない
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.68,0:11:52.72,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,本当にやるの
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.94,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ちゃんと策はあるんだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,信じてるからね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,振り落とされるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.49,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,早く策を実行しろ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,一瞬で済むことだ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大したことじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリンの痛みに
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,比べれば
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.77,0:12:44.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.09,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どこ行くの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,墓場に幽霊が出るんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.42,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,父さんたちには秘密だからな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だって
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あんまりくっつくと　歩きづらいだろ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.28,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,虫一匹いないな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.82,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,帰ろう　ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃん　兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.10,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,取ってくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,助けて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.88,Dialogue_JP_Alt,,0,0,0,,頼む
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.96,Dialogue_JP_Alt,,0,0,0,,取ってくれ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.43,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,冷たい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,息ができない
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリン　逃げ…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.65,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,兄ちゃんを
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.39,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,放せー
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.34,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そこのお墓の人
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,指輪が魂を縛ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,取ってあげて
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,霊は解放される
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,指輪？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いったい…
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.44,0:15:35.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これ　先日死んだオルマンの墓だ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.62,0:15:39.75,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,生前よく自慢してた　エルフから金の指輪を買ったと
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なぜそんなことを　あの子どもは
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私何か悪いことした
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.16,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,すごいことだよ　ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,お前は霊術の才能があるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気にすんな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.92,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大人は魔法が怖いもんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリンはちゃんとした魔法を勉強したらいい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.09,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,仕事に困らないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,仕事？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.40,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.85,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,司祭とか　墓守とか
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.49,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,旅の除霊師ってのもおもしろそうだな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.52,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,外国を渡り歩いて　困ってる人を助けるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,楽しそう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そしたら兄ちゃんも一緒に来てくれる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もっちろん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.47,0:16:23.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どんな国に行ってみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,海が見たいな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.57,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,砂漠でもいい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,砂漠には喋る犬の国があるらしい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.12,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,絶対行きたい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.22,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.17,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう一緒には行かないほうがいいかもしれないね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.06,0:16:42.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリン
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,どうして
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.52,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,気にしなくていいの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,さよなら　ライオス兄さん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.70,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオス　大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.21,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ひとまず止血だけしておくから
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.74,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,もう少し我慢してね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私　２人を探してくる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あと　脚も
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,「気にしないで」か
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.33,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな悲しいこと言うなよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.12,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,絶対に連れて帰るからな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.76,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,チルチャック
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.70,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,センシ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.01,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いた
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よかった
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.43,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,じゃないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.55,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,私も　防御魔法もっと練習しなきゃな
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,まっ　破裂してないだけ上出来だ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.41,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,トロンサム　ルナァエ　スタンティヌス
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.66,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ユーレカント　ウーンズゥ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.75,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,いってえ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.59,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,余計苦しんでないか
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.73,0:17:54.00,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大ケガを短時間で治すと　回復痛がね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.18,0:17:57.07,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　ちゃんと治ってる証しだから
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　次はセンシ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ワシはいい
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.20,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,自分で治す
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.91,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,何か月かかるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリンは回復魔法が得意だったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,でも私だって　早さには自信があるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.27,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そ…　それが痛みの原因では
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.11,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ライオース
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほら　足出して
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.58,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ブリトレイトウームス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.04,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ルナァエ　アクトゥム
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,アスバム　ヒストゥム　エレス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.95,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ユーレカント　ウーンズゥ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.23,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,くっついた
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.85,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,足の中がかゆい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,回復痛　回復痛
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.04,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よくやったな　ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.30,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,本当に炎竜を倒しおった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.27,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,みんなのおかげだ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.93,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,誰一人欠けてもこの勝ちはなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.81,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,一時はどうなることかと思ったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.02,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,さすがに肝が冷えた
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.32,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,想定が少し甘かったな
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.25,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,まっ　勝てりゃいいんだ　勝てりゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.16,0:19:02.77,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ただ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほれ　ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ケン助
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.08,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,その件については　まだ許してないからな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.51,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あとでゆっくり話をさせろ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.98,0:19:12.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.69,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,さて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.37,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,腹の中身を確認してみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.63,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,分厚い皮膚
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これじゃ包丁で戦っても
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,皮下脂肪にすら届かないわけだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.54,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,しかし　胃に辿りつくまで一仕事だな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.13,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,発破かけてみる
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.73,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,竜もさすがに内臓は他の生き物と同じだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.38,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,少しずつ肉を掘りながら進もう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あばら骨だ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,少し迂回して掘り進めよう
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,暗いな　ランタンをつけるか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.35,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,火はだめだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.31,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,マルシル　明かりを
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.79,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,あっつ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.44,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,炭鉱で働いていた時代を思い出すな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.56,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.36,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,胃袋だ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.03,0:20:29.68,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,よし
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.14,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,開くぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.98,0:20:41.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,空…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.97,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.67,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,違う竜なんじゃないの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.15,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それはない
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.90,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,目の上の傷は確かにあのときの竜と同じものだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.60,0:20:58.42,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,縄張り意識の強いオスが　こんな近くに何匹もいるとは考えにくいし
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.18,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,念のため腸もさらってみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.18,0:21:06.06,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほ…　骨の一片も残ってないなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.85,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,急いで　フンを探さなきゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.83,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,不眠で動き続けたことで消化が進んだか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.27,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.45,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,何これ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.05,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,毛や骨の塊だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.60,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,獲物を丸飲みする動物の一部は
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.04,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,消化しにくいものをまとめて吐き出すんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.06,0:21:51.84,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,炎竜はそれを吐き出さず　炎の息の燃料にする
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.47,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この黒い毛は何匹か魔狼を食ってるな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.02,0:21:56.86,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それに…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.78,0:22:02.24,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,か…　髪の毛
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.00,0:22:03.89,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,それって…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.04,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ほぐしてみよう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.61,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,人骨が混じっているかもしれない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.53,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,なあ　この棒って
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.62,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ちょっと　ライオス
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.92,0:22:17.81,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,この杖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.96,0:22:23.64,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファ…
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.48,0:22:26.46,Dialogue_JP,,0,0,0,,ファリン
Dialogue: 2,0:00:08.26,0:00:09.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这样就准备好了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,可以随时让这建筑崩塌
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.08,0:00:17.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,魔力还很充足
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.84,0:00:21.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这下就算莱欧斯他们出现了意外 我也能帮一下
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.78,0:00:24.88,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这样应该没有问题吧
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.71,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,用尽所有的魔力 让龙昏迷
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,比起需要大家拼命 还不知道能不能命中的爆炸魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,把龙埋在建筑下面的方案稳妥多了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 这个方案要好多了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.23,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,冷静一些
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.84,0:00:48.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我必须完成好自己的任务
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.87,0:00:51.30,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.13,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,等着我 法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,发现我们了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.04,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.92,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,也太快了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,顺便一提 红龙最快时速60公里
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.91,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你早说啊
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,它受到地形的限制 没事
Dialogue: 2,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,下个路口右转
Dialogue: 2,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.67,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,在这直道引诱它喷火
Dialogue: 2,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.95,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龙通过咂嘴点燃体内的燃料 进而喷火
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.22,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,防止它被控制住以后发狂
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.09,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要让它在路上吐出所有的燃料
Dialogue: 2,0:03:31.34,0:03:32.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,舌头动了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.07,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要喷火了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好强的热浪
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.11,0:03:40.75,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,能借助锅和魔法抗住
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好 这样下去…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.37,0:03:55.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.75,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,锅的热量…
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.00,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,均匀扩散…
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 2,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.32,0:04:17.00,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西每天都在用那东西做饭
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,还以为能排斥龙的火焰呢
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.09,0:04:24.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,娜玛莉不是说 精金能够防御住龙的所有攻击
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.98,0:04:27.03,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那家伙随便乱说是吧
Dialogue: 2,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我没说
Dialogue: 2,0:04:31.81,0:04:32.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,又要来了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.01,0:04:33.88,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,改变路线
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.98,0:04:44.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 2,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.13,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这就来了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.92,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,有点快啊
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不是打算分头行动吗
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我按照计划行动就行吗
Dialogue: 2,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好烦 不管了
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我直接动手
Dialogue: 2,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,完全没效果啊
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.12,0:05:57.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,逆鳞就在跟前
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.55,0:06:12.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,再向前走一点
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,就够了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么逃走了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,该死 剑助
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.30,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,魔物终究是魔物…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.09,0:06:31.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 2,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯 奇尔查克 起来
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看上面
Dialogue: 2,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.98,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,去肚子下面
Dialogue: 2,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯 你这家伙
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.92,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怪我 是我不好
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.37,0:06:44.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,该死 通用语言骂人的话太少了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.58,0:06:46.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Ponza Toroldo Unerma!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么开始用我不懂的语言骂我了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,接下来怎么办啊
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,生气了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,它真的好生气
Dialogue: 2,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.01,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没办法了 从尾巴旁边溜出…
Dialogue: 2,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.67,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不行 好危险
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.79,0:07:05.49,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要一辈子走不出这两腿之间了
Dialogue: 2,0:07:08.88,0:07:09.80,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.95,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这么简单的咒语没有效果
Dialogue: 2,0:07:12.11,0:07:12.88,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,专心
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.43,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.79,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,唯一的武器都碎了…
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,接下来怎么办啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没办法了 拿去用吧
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.92,0:07:36.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那真是用特殊金属制作的吗
Dialogue: 2,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,斩断任何魔物的骨与皮
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.22,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我日复一日 从未忘记打磨
Dialogue: 2,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这世上或许仅此一把
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.64,0:07:46.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,秘银制作的菜刀
Dialogue: 2,0:07:47.33,0:07:48.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,秘银?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 2,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真想给娜玛莉看看
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.96,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那家伙搞不好会杀了先西啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我隐约有那样的预感 所以就没提起
Dialogue: 2,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.71,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 2,0:08:04.87,0:08:06.96,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的刺穿了鳞片
Dialogue: 2,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.84,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不过这刀就这么点 不管砍哪个位置
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.70,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么想都无法造成致命伤吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.97,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.30,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看起来计划是失败了?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,还是说在执行其他方案?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.50,0:08:34.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.98,0:08:38.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没有时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,退后 退后
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.99,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,武器离我们越来越远
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,再向后就要到广场上了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.99,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一口火就给我们喷成渣
Dialogue: 2,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我来吸引龙的注意力
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,别 太危险
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.30,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯 你该明白了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:57.95,0:09:00.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你过去吃下的所有魔物
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.51,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,哪个不是拼尽了全力
Dialogue: 2,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,在这里 不是吃就是被吃
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,如果不竭尽全力 我们就是沦为食物的一方
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,咬紧牙关
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.13,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先…
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.13,0:09:26.81,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.16,0:09:29.20,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你跑出去还有什么意义
Dialogue: 2,0:09:29.79,0:09:31.07,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你先撤退
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,和玛露希尔想想办法
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.99,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,喂 还活着吗
Dialogue: 2,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我拉你出来…
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.49,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,能动吗
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.76,0:09:55.53,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么好像粘到地上…
Dialogue: 2,0:10:02.73,0:10:04.16,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.17,0:10:08.20,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.80,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 2,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先…
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 玛露希尔
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没想到你在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.71,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,还好 看来我的魔法还有效
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,现在什么情况
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.53,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,他们两个呢
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.07,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,情况变得很不妙
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,所有计划都失败了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,他们两个倒在了龙跟前
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.87,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎怎… 怎么办
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这样吗 只有我的魔法了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龙受了伤 现在很狂躁
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.34,0:10:55.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,靠近或是进入它的视线都很危险
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.80,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,可如果不抓紧时间的话…
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,去上面
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要… 要做什么
Dialogue: 2,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.09,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,到龙头部的高度
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我站在锅里
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.78,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,玛露希尔对锅使用爆炸魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.09,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龙的左眼已经瞎了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,从左侧靠近的话
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.75,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,应该可以趁它没察觉跳上去
Dialogue: 2,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.87,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这也太…
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,玛露希尔之前也做过同样的事吧
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,与温蒂妮战斗的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.14,0:11:30.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那时有水 还有水上行走的魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这次有防御魔法和锅
Dialogue: 2,0:11:33.34,0:11:34.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那接下来呢
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你抱在它的头上 怎么瞄准逆鳞
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我有个主意
Dialogue: 2,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没有失败的余地了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我会成功
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.68,0:11:52.72,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的要来吗
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.94,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的想好办法了吗
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要被甩出去了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.49,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,必须赶快动手
Dialogue: 2,0:12:30.95,0:12:32.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一瞬间就能完成
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,比起法琳的痛
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不算什么
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.77,0:12:44.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.09,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,听说墓地里有幽灵出现
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.42,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不要告诉爸爸他们哦
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你抱得这么紧 我怎么走路
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.28,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,虫子都没见一只
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.82,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,回去吧 法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.10,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,帮我取掉
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.02,0:14:42.88,Dialogue_CN_Alt,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.43,0:14:44.96,Dialogue_CN_Alt,,0,0,0,,帮我取掉
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.43,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 2,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,无法呼吸
Dialogue: 2,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳 快逃
Dialogue: 2,0:14:51.92,0:14:53.65,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,把哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.39,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.34,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那边墓里的人
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,戒指束缚了灵魂
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.10,0:15:24.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,帮他取下来
Dialogue: 2,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,灵魂会得到解脱
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,戒指?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,究竟…
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.44,0:15:35.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这是前几天去世的奥尔曼的墓
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.62,0:15:39.75,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,生前经常炫耀 说从精灵那买来了金戒指
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那个孩子怎么会知道…
Dialogue: 2,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我做了坏事吗
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.16,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,很厉害呀 法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你有使用灵术的才能
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.63,0:15:55.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.92,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,大人都害怕魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.84,0:16:01.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳去好好学习一下魔法就行
Dialogue: 2,0:16:01.62,0:16:03.09,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不愁没有工作
Dialogue: 2,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,工作?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.40,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.68,0:16:07.85,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,司祭 要么守墓人?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:08.15,0:16:10.49,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,做个四处旅行的除灵师也很有趣吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.12,0:16:16.52,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,在国外四处游历 帮助有困难的人
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好像很有意思
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那哥哥也会与我一起去吗
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.47,0:16:23.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你想去什么样的国家
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.00,0:16:27.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,想看看大海
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.57,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,沙漠也不错
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,听说沙漠里有会说话的狗的国家
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.12,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我想去看看
Dialogue: 2,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.22,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.17,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我们或许不该再一同踏上旅途了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:42.06,0:16:42.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.52,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,再见了 莱欧斯哥哥
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.70,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯 没事吧
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.21,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我先帮你止一下血
Dialogue: 2,0:16:59.38,0:17:00.74,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你再坚持一会
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我去找他们两个
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,还有你的腿
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,「不用在意我」吗
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.87,0:17:12.33,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不要说这么悲伤的话
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.12,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我一定会带你回去
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.76,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,奇尔查克
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.70,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,先西
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.01,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你在这
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:27.76,0:17:28.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.43,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看起来不像
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.55,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我还需要好好练习一下防御魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,身体没破裂已经算是很好了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.41,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Tronsum Lunaae Stantinus
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.92,0:17:43.66,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Eurekant Oonzu
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.75,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.59,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,他是不是更痛苦了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:50.73,0:17:54.00,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,短时间内治愈大伤 会有恢复痛
Dialogue: 2,0:17:54.18,0:17:57.07,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不用担心 这说明是治好了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,现在该先西了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:58.56,0:17:59.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.20,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我自己能好
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.91,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,要花几个月啊
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳很擅长恢复的魔法
Dialogue: 2,0:18:05.38,0:18:08.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,但比速度 我还是有信心的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.27,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这… 这就是痛苦的原因…
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.11,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,来 把腿抬起来
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.58,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Britrayeums
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.04,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Lunae Actum
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Asbam Histum Eres
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.95,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,Eurekant Ounzu
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.23,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,接上了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.08,0:18:38.85,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,腿里面好痒
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.85,0:18:40.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,恢复痛 恢复痛
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.92,0:18:43.04,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,你做得不错 莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.30,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,真的把红龙打败了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.27,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,多亏了大家
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.47,0:18:50.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,少了谁这场战斗都无法胜利
Dialogue: 2,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.81,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,之前都差点就以为要完蛋了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.05,0:18:56.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,捏了一把冷汗
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.32,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,计划还是欠考虑了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.66,0:19:01.25,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,算了 赢了就行 赢了就好
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.16,0:19:02.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,拿好 莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:19:05.13,0:19:05.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,剑助
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.27,0:19:09.08,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,关于这件事 我可还没有原谅你
Dialogue: 2,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.51,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,之后我们好好谈谈
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.98,0:19:12.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.69,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.37,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,检查一下肚子里面吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.63,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好厚的皮肤
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,拿着菜刀来战斗
Dialogue: 2,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,确实连皮下脂肪都碰不到
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.54,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,看这样想走到胃里也不容易啊
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.13,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,爆破一下试试?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.73,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,龙的内脏也与其他生物的差不多
Dialogue: 2,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.38,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一边挖肉一边前进吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,是肋骨
Dialogue: 2,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我们换个方向绕一下吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好黑 点个提灯吧
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.46,0:20:03.35,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不能用火
Dialogue: 2,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.31,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,玛露希尔 照明
Dialogue: 2,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.79,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.44,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,回想起了在煤矿工作的日子
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.36,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,是胃
Dialogue: 2,0:20:29.03,0:20:29.68,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 2,0:20:30.27,0:20:31.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,打开看看
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.98,0:20:41.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,空的…
Dialogue: 2,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.97,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.13,0:20:46.67,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,找错龙了?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.15,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这不会
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.59,0:20:51.90,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,眼睛上方的伤与那时的龙一模一样
Dialogue: 2,0:20:53.60,0:20:58.42,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,地盘意识这么强的雄性 这附近应该不会同时出现好几头
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.18,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,保险起见 肠子也掏一遍吧
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.18,0:21:06.06,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,连… 连一块骨头都没剩下…
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.85,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间 去看看粪便
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.83,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,不睡觉一直活动 所以消化很快吗
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.27,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.45,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.05,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,一团头发与骨头
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.60,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,有些将猎物整个吞下的动物
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.04,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,会将难以消化的部分集中吐出去
Dialogue: 2,0:21:48.06,0:21:51.84,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,但红龙不会吐 而是用来做吐息的燃料
Dialogue: 2,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.47,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这黑毛是吃了几头座狼
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.02,0:21:56.86,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.78,0:22:02.24,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,是… 是头发
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.00,0:22:03.89,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这么说…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.04,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,摊开看看吧
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.61,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,或许里面有人的骨头
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.53,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,我说 这根棒子…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.11,0:22:16.62,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,过来看看 莱欧斯
Dialogue: 2,0:22:16.92,0:22:17.81,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,这法杖
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.96,0:22:23.64,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法…
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.48,0:22:26.46,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,法琳?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:08.08,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,外から窓をくぐった光が　床に作った最初の友達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:15.38,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,空っぽの手を容易く取られて　連れ出されてから夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:23.05,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,幾つかの普通が重なり合うと　時々そこには魔法が宿る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:30.52,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,あれは恐らく悪魔だった　あれから醒めない夢の中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:34.32,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,籠の中　鳥が鳴いて気付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:39.86,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,失くしていた事　もう引き返せない事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:49.08,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,どうして体は生きたがるの　心に何を求めているの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:56.63,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,肺が吸い込んだ　続きの世界　何度でも吐いた　命の証
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:04.18,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,さあ今　鍵が廻る音　探し物が囁くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:12.35,Meshi_OPJP,,0,0,0,,赤い血が巡る　その全てで　見えない糸を手繰り寄せて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:08.08,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,窗外的一缕光线洒落地面 是最初的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:15.38,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,空无一物的手就这样被握紧 启程便是梦境之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:23.05,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,一次次平凡的遭遇 魔法也时而蕴藏其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:30.52,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,那恐怕便是恶魔 从此便是难以苏醒的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.06,0:01:34.32,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,笼中的鸟儿啼鸣 回过神来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:39.86,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,失去的事物 无法挽回的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:49.08,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,为何身体不肯放弃生存 内心在向往什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:56.63,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,用力吸气 今后的世界 无数次吐气 生命的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:02:04.18,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,现在钥匙转动的声音响起 寻找之物就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:12.35,Meshi_OPCN,,0,0,0,,血液涌上 一切的一切 收起无法看见的丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:36.03,Meshi_EDJP,,888,0,0,,{\blur2}君のためのパーティーだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:46.38,Meshi_EDJP,,0,1070,0,,{\blur2}どこから話すべきかな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:51.72,Meshi_EDJP,,0,1070,0,,{\blur2}君にはそういつも救われてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:58.22,Meshi_EDJP,,0,820,1,,{\blur2}だから今日こそはとびきりをプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:00.98,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}さぁ始めるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.77,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}着慣れてないドレスコード
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:06.77,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}お馴染みの顔がお出迎え
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.15,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}君のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.78,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}みんなが想っているんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:13.11,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,1,,{\blur2}Full-course session
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:15.49,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,1,,{\blur2}※リアクションはノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.49,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,1,,{\blur2}ボナペティート！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:22.75,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}「ありがとう」じゃ足らんなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.50,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}それ以上なら何だっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.75,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ただ君に伝われ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:30.63,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}ふざけ合って笑う時も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.51,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}涙こぼれそうな夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.51,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}君のための仲間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.47,Meshi_EDJP,,777,0,0,,{\blur2}それはどんな魔法だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:41.35,Meshi_EDJP,,777,0,0,,{\blur2}超えるような希望のフレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:44.27,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}ただ君が笑うだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.35,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}だから今日は騒いだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:49.27,Meshi_EDJP,,0,777,0,,{\blur2}誰も文句は言わせない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:51.98,Meshi_EDJP,,888,0,0,,{\blur2}君のためのパーティーだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.98,0:23:55.53,Meshi_EDJP,,888,0,0,,{\blur2}楽しもうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:23:58.87,Meshi_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2}いいから跳んじゃって！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:36.03,Meshi_EDCN,,888,0,0,,都是为你准备的聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:46.38,Meshi_EDCN,,0,1070,0,,该从何处说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:51.72,Meshi_EDCN,,0,1070,0,,一路总是得到你的拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:58.22,Meshi_EDCN,,0,820,1,,所以今天要送你一份惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:00.98,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:03.77,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,不习惯的衣着打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:06.77,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,熟悉的朋友前来迎接
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.15,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.78,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,大家何时曾经忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:13.11,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,1,,Full-course session
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:15.49,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,1,,※反应并非虚构
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.49,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,1,,用餐愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:22.75,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,「谢谢」还不足够
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.50,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,在此之上怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:28.75,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,只要理解便好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:30.63,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,打闹也好欢笑也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:33.51,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,打湿眼眶的夜晚也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:36.51,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,大家都是你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.47,Meshi_EDCN,,777,0,0,,无论怎样的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:41.35,Meshi_EDCN,,777,0,0,,都难比拟的希望的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:44.27,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,只要看到你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.35,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,今天就尽情喧闹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:49.27,Meshi_EDCN,,0,777,0,,没有人能有意见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.27,0:23:51.98,Meshi_EDCN,,888,0,0,,都是为你准备的聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.98,0:23:55.53,Meshi_EDCN,,888,0,0,,开心尽兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:23:58.87,Meshi_EDCN,,0,0,0,,就来跳起来吧
